    "## 6. Winner selection\n",
    "\n",
    "Rule: of the distribution-driven strategies whose coreg coverage is ≥ 0.95 on **every** subject, pick the one with the highest `threshold_min` across subjects (tie-break by `threshold_mean`). Baseline is excluded from the ranking (kept as a reference only)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "474a7b74",
   "metadata": {},
